00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:54,000
They responded very positively.

200
00:25:54,000 --> 00:26:03,000
They were mostly older guys who oftentimes prays us for what we were doing.

201
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:08,000
And kind of acted as big brothers to us, you know, protected us.

202
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:15,000
If there was someone who wanted to harm us, you know, then they were quite, quite receptive to us.

203
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:17,000
And we looked upon them as...

204
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:22,000
