205
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:30,000
We think that was an opportunity to bring them into the fold, you know, and to talk about the conditions on which they got the end of the first place.

206
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:32,000
To do some organizing.

207
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,000
Exactly.

208
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:36,000
A great place to organize.

209
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:38,000
It's a matter of fact.

210
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,000
You have a cap of bodies.

211
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,000
Exactly.

212
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:43,000
So you do your time.

213
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:44,000
You survive.

214
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:45,000
Yes.

215
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:48,000
You make it through.

216
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:50,000
What do you remember coming out?

217
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:52,000
