228
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:24,000
But I also worked in other counties around the counties as well.

229
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:26,000
Continue doing voter registration.

230
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:30,000
Continue doing...

231
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:34,000
Testing the laws of the public, the combination of what have you.

