00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:26,000
And the restroom was outside.

246
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:29,000
He had to go outside and go around to the side of the building.

247
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:33,000
While we were waiting, no one came to take our order.

248
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:38,000
But about 10 minutes passed, we noticed that he hadn't come back from the restroom.

249
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:44,000
So we finally got up and sat to get up and leave.

250
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:47,000
And as we get up to leave to go to the car,

251
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:52,000
we met by a group of whites who would come across the street from a service station with tire arms.

252
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:55,000
And they had a lot of tire arms and...

253
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:58,000
And baseball bats.

254
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:01,000
And so they waited until we got into the car,

